%p
  We’re thrilled to invite you to join our elite group of 10,000 founding members. 

%p
  To start taking advantage of the unforgettable dining experiences we have to offer, complete your membership application now.

%p
  You have two payment options for your membership fees:
  %table{:cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "margin:10px 0 0;"}
    %tr
      -Subscription::PLANS.each do |name, plan|
        %td
          %a{:href => new_membership_url(:plan => name)}
            %table{:cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "border:1px solid #999;"}
              %tr
                %td{:style => "text-align:center;padding:5px 0;color:#fff;background:#999"}
                  =name
              %tr
                %td{:style => "text-align:center;font-size:25px;padding:5px 10px;margin: 5px 0;"}
                  =plan.payment_summary        
              %tr
                %td{:style => "text-align:center; padding:5px 10px;"}
                  %p{:style => "margin: 5px 0;padding:0;"}
                    -if plan.period == "monthly"
                      ="Monthly Membership"
                    -else
                      ="Annual Membership"
                  %p{:style => "margin: 5px 0;padding:0;"} 
                    -if plan.period == "monthly"
                      ="Cancel Anytime"
                    -else
                      %span{:style=>"font-weight:bold;"}="Save 40%"
        %td{:style => "width:10px;"}
%p
  Our signup process is quick and secure, and don’t forget about 
  ="#{link_to "the Spot Guarantee", policies_url}.".html_safe

%p
  Contact us with any questions – we’re here to help!
  %ul{:style => "list-style:none;margin:10px 0;padding:0;"}
    %li="Mail : #{mail_to "contact@spot-app.com"}".html_safe
    %li="Phone: #{PHONE_NUMBER}"

%p Sincerely,
%p{:style => "margin:0;padding:0;"} Julia & The Spot Team
